1. After assessment, user rates confidence (0-5)
   ↓
2. Frontend: POST /api/srs/review {topic_name, quality}
   ↓
3. Backend SM-2 Algorithm:
   ├─ Find or create SRSCard
   ├─ Calculate new srs_n, srs_ef, srs_interval
   ├─ Set srs_next_review date
   ├─ Log review in SRSReview (audit trail)
   ↓
4. Return next review date
   ↓
5. Topic scheduled for future review

══════════════════════════════════════

1. Next day (or after srs_interval days)
   ↓
2. User checks /srs/due?syllabus_id=5
   ↓
3. Backend queries: srs_next_review <= TODAY
   ↓
4. Returns due topics in priority order
   ↓
5. User can review topics again